      "date": "2012-09-10 07:56:30.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/faa8337e-fb1c-11e1-b108-52540035b04c).  Ran 1 tests.  No failures.",
